{"tid":1048354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(網上投票)西甲官方第26輪MVP評選：武磊PK莫拉達、比基","createTime":"2019-03-05T14:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T06:39:58.000Z","uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"95258338e11bbc7243cc581534d2405b9addf006","tid":1048354,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"時間3月5日晚，西甲聯賽官方公佈了聯賽第26輪的最佳球員候選名單，剛剛收穫西甲個人首球、創造中國足球歷史的武磊進入候選名單，他的競爭對手有前鋒斯圖亞尼、莫拉達以及後衛比基。<br />\n<br />\n各位吧友可以點此西甲本輪最佳球員評選，為武磊投票。<br />\n<br />\n四名候選人員如下：<br />\n<br />\n斯圖亞尼（赫羅納）&mdash;&mdash;梅開二度<br />\n<br />\n比基（巴塞）&mdash;&mdash;呈現完美打比<br />\n<br />\n莫拉達（馬體會）&mdash;&mdash;梅開二度<br />\n<br />\n武磊（愛斯賓奴）&mdash;&mdash;收穫西甲首球<br />\n<br />\n（六月）"},{"pid":"de49ad29eaa7c8604b37f86e9c53125868695b1c","tid":1048354,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.laliga.es/noticias/elige-al-mvp-de-la-jornada-26-de-laliga-santander\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.laliga.es%2Fnoticias%2Felige-al-mvp-de-la-jornada-26-de-laliga-santander&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=90b6e7e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.laliga.es/noticias/elige-al-mvp-de-la-jornada-26-de-laliga-santander</a>"},{"pid":"3ddb30f3aa82bd75e9afe8bdce08888c7493de75","tid":1048354,"uid":160589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"碧基"},{"pid":"9b1a57ad1b84525d56336e717fc8f44ff783a0e5","tid":1048354,"uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/225311_0b988ffb4277bc74dcc8932f26ff9871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F225311_0b988ffb4277bc74dcc8932f26ff9871.jpg&h=26f1b556&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cd4a659b8df2ce46e8e4baee251a3acd3b7834e","tid":1048354,"uid":5652